{
  "stem": "24212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what was very nice, we walked to work and from work, which gave us some exercise and, sort of, we could look.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were with SS guards, nevertheless.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But at least we could see color, and once in awhile, we see-- could see people on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the factory had some German civilians, like the old Meister, who must have been 70.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was the top boss.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was sort of a-- a good guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think that he didn't agree with all this prisoner business that he had to supervise.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not that he wasn't a, you know, a Nazi, but I don't think he agreed that people should be forced to do things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then there was the young master, who was a son of a bitch, but he was lame and that's why he was at home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to watch out for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When he came around, everybody was working like mad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then were local women, also, additional workers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But everybody who wasn't us was a supervisor, you know, we had to watch out for.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had three layers of people above us, and in the door, always, stood the SS, you know, with either a holster, a gun, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Watching.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where they got these SS women, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that some of them were maids before, or washer women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And yet, they put the uniform on them, and they had the power of life and death over thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The could shoot you and nothing happened to them in the line of duty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, Gross Rosen was OK in this subdivision.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Funny, I wanted to go back there, too, and we couldn't find the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I knew the name of the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
